Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:19.24,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,A world in which the Titans \Nattack and devour humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:24.08,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,The humans, who became the hunted...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:30.05,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,built big walls and lived behind them in \Nexchange for their freedom to prevent invasion.{erected→Built  ??}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:40.60,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,However, the fragile peace was destroyed with the appearance of the Colossal Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, Mikasa! You two need to live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:17.22,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger, whose mother\N had been killed by a Titan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:22.43,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,became a trainee to polish his knowledge and\N skills necessary to exterminate the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:28.48,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,He and his fellow 104th Training Corps,\N who spent three years together training,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:32.86,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,would need to be determined\N to fight against the Titans. {determine their resolution  ??}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:36.99,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,We already have the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:40.87,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Humanity can't defeat the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.29,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,And...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:51.13,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,You want us to waste the knowledge we have derived through thousands of deaths {tactics ??}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.92,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,and become food for the Titans?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:55.21,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,No way in Hell! {No way in Hell ??}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:02:01.72,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,I'm going to join the Survey Corps and exterminate the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we recapture the land, we'll be \Nable to raise more cows and sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Humanity is finally regaining its dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mankind's retaliation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}begins now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:34.05,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,A deadly battle took place in the Trost District against the Titans who appeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:36.05,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:42.39,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Humanity broke its chains of fear and faced forward with their knowledge. {Wisdome ?? }
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:54.61,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,But, a new discovery brought back fear to mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Recruit Jaeger?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you seal that gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just as clueless as \Nthe rest of us present here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's true, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the wrong question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you do it or not—which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:37.69,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Will Eren Jaeger, who had obtained the power to turn into a Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.78,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,be the savior of mankind...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:44.16,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,or a demon that leads mankind to destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer already, scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to join the Survey Corps
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and slaughter some Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:35.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1648,3108)\blur8\fs55\pos(983.2,858)\3c&H3E42C1&\c&H3E42C1&\bord1.82\shad1.21\fnSnKsign\1a&HFF&\t(1603,1648,\1a&H00&)\t(4442,4487,\1a&HFF&)}[{\fscx70}  {\fscx}Part II{\fscx70}  {\fscx}]  {\fscx550\fscy110}-{\fscx\fscy\1a}{\fscx70}  {\fscx}Wings of Freedom{\fscx60}  {\fscx}{\fscx550\fscy110}-{\fscx}
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.33,0:04:35.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1648,0)\blur1\fs55\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\fnSnKsign\pos(983.2,858)\t(4442,0,1,\c&H060606&)}[{\fscx70}  {\fscx}Part II{\fscx70}  {\fscx}]  {\fscx550\fscy110\1a&H3A&}-{\fscx\fscy\1a}{\fscx70}  {\fscx}Wings of Freedom{\fscx60}  {\fscx}{\fscx550\fscy110\1a&H3A&}-{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:07.20,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,That hurt, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:12.54,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Can't you go a little easier on others?! {Don't you have a little thing called consideration for others?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:18.42,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,It's because you come at me with full\N power that I have to act accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:26.43,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,If you consider yourself a man, shouldn't\N you go easier on this fragile body of mine? {If you consider yourself a man, ?? }
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:27.05,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.97,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Your jokes aren't funny, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:34.43,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,If you're weaker than me, then why am I\N on the ground and you're still standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:43.48,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,It isn't like I threw you with force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.65,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,The weak have to use \Nself-protection techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.99,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,to protect themselves against those who are stronger than them, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:55.50,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,It won't hurt you to know these kind of moves, too. {You won't lose out on knowing these.  ?? }
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:58.04,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,I understand, but let's take a break first, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:58.96,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Here I go! {Let's go! ?? }
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:13.10,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Annie... I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.60,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,I give up... { I give up, you hear...?  ??}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.81,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.39,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:20.61,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Learn how to use your strength... {I don't need you to give up ??}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.98,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,...and how to talk to girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:26.03,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Ok, I'll learn how. Let me go already! {remember/memorized instead of learn ??}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:29.24,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Really? You want to learn more?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.75,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Why the hell did you come flying, Reiner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.71,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Hey, Annie...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.34,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Can you teach those moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.64,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,...to me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:05.07,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,I don't know about that. \NThese moves are only for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:08.03,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,I don't think someone like you needs them at all. {don't think someone like you - seems more fit}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:14.78,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,But, I'm curious whether these moves will work on a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:18.20,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,I...Is this for real? At last...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.25,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.83,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Are they gonna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:23.29,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,It's the most anticipated duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.13,Default Alt,NEW,0,0,0,,W...Which one do you think?  {too long ??} {Which one wins?} { "Who's going to win?" or "Who'll win?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.21,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Do you think it will be Annie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.55,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.80,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,I bet my whole dinner on Mikasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.68,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Which one do you think will win, Eren? { Which one would you pick, Eren? ??}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.05,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.81,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Which one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:13.80,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I remembering that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.76,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what the others are doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.69,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.65,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{\i1}...where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.19,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many days have passed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:33.03,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{\i1}How long is this confinement going to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please bear with this for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll try to sort things out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:43.12,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,807)\i1}Commander Erwin said that but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I stuck here for good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Eren, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay? Feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free to come out of there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's assuming you wear these though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Hange Zoe, a Squad Leader\Nin the Survey Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The same goes for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Mike Zacharias.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a habit of smelling people \Nhe's met for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and snorting afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure it's nothing more than just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, sorry for wasting all our time\N only talking about insignificant things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, going in clueless is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's selfish of us, but we...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,can only put our faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Best of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A courthouse?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was under a courthouse?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are these people here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,513)\i1}What's going to be decided anyway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You guys...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a soldier who has \Noffered his life for mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that accurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an unprecedented case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The trial will be a special court-martial \Nin which common law does not apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us begin with the Military Police \NBrigade's opening statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your honor, after conducting a thorough examination of Eren's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,we dispose of him in a prompt manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It cannot be denied that his Titan power \Nallowed us to repel the latest attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However, his existence is also a source \Nof discord that can incite rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, after having him impart all the information he can provide,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have him die as a hero of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let us hear the\NSurvey Corps' opening statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We of the Survey Corps will accept \NEren as an official member
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and use his Titan power to recapture Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If we utilize his power, \Nwe can recapture Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it's clear what needs to be prioritized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be best to seal \Nall the gates for good now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The only parts of the wall the Colossus \NTitan can destroy are the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already, you boor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You want mere humans to tamper \Nwith Wall Rose, a gift from God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough out of you, priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Order in the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You may argue about differences \Nin principles elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaeger, allow me to confirm:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you continue to contribute to mankind as you have thus far
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and utilize your Titan power to that same end?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the report for the\NBattle of Trost District, it said:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"After transforming into a Titan, \Nhe swung his fist at Mikasa Ackerman."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you wanted me to lie in a report?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mikasa Ackerman here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that Jaeger attacked\Nyou in his Titan form?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, a Titan will\Nalways be a Titan, after all.{He's like the rest of them, after all. -Evetaku}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tried to kill Mikasa?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa Ackerman lost her parents at a young \Nage and was taken in by the Jaeger family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, through our investigations,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we have uncovered some shocking events \Nthat took place during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At the age of nine, Eren Jaegar and Mikasa Ackerman
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,138)} stabbed to death three men wanted for robbery and kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Though this falls under legitimate self-defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel their basic human nature needs to be questioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be a Titan that's been hiding \Namongst us in the form of a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised if she wasn't human!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We should dissect her just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be a monster, but that \Nhas nothing to do with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As if we could trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's covering for her because it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, all of you've been doing is blurting out\N convenient speculations that suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you've never even {\i1}seen{\i0} a Titan before,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so what are you so afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should't say any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I'll keep at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make my stand here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we afford to not\Nlet those with power fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're scared of fighting to survive, \Nthen lend me your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You... damn cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,227)}Just shut up and bet everything on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just my pet theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think pain and \Ndiscipline go hand-in-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What you need now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't a lecture, but training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a good position for me to kick too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Levi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll you do if he gets \Nangry and transforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are gonna dissect him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Supreme Commander, I have a proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren's Titan power has \Nmany uncertain points to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,which poses a constant threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So I propose he be entrusted \Nto Lance Corporal Levi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and taken out on an expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll bring Eren outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like Eren's control over his Titan power,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and his worth to mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to be judged based on the\Nresults of that expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Handling Eren Jaeger...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it, Levi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain I could kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is that there'll be no alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:21.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(688,805)\b1\fnCardo\c&H000000&\blur2\alpha&H10&\fscy90\fscx90\pos(962.25,667.333)}A Few Days Later
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.10,0:17:21.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(688,805)\b1\blur0.4\fnCardo\c&HEFEFEF&\fscy90\fscx90\pos(960,664.333)}A Few Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The former Survey Corps HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As an old castle that was renovated to be our base,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it definitely looks extravagant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But since it's this far away \Nfrom the walls and the river,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it really wasn't something we needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined we'd be keeping \Nyou in that old decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get ahead of yourself, recruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be a Titan or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but a pissy brat like you being under \NLance Corporal Levi's watch—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you get for \Nyapping away on horseback.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,First impressions are crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That recruit was scared stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, that's not how you usually talk, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If... If that's your idea of \Nimitating Lance Corporal Levi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,could you seriously stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, it's not like\Nit was similar in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to keep me down, Petra?{control?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't gone through the \Nproper steps to act as my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you had bit your tongue off and died...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These people are the Survey \NCorps' Special-Ops Squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a.k.a. The Levi Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're all elites that were \Nhand-picked by Lance Corporal Levi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if I go berserk, they'll be the ones to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There are weeds everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The inside's probably covered in dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}that's{\i0} a problem we can't overlook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get to work immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The upper floor is clean now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of the rooms should I stay in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're to stay in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The basement again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've yet to gain full control over yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you accidentally transform into a Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we can restrain you as long \Nas you're underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one of the conditions given \Nto us in exchange for your custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rule to be followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a look upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, you finish up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,An expedition to establish a base\Nfor a supply chain in thirty days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want us to bring the\Nnewly graduated recruits along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's assuming any of them enlist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, I'd have to say this seems too rushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren's current position is only temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to prove to Central that he's\Nbeneficial to mankind as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, the Military Police\NBrigade might interfere again—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be honest, even with me, Erwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as sharp as ever, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still not at your level though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you when the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to start, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we're ready, we'll fire a smoke signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do after that is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This dry well will be able to restrain \Na Titan even if it's out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:23.59,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,We've been studying captured \NTitans like Sawney and Bean,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:27.93,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,but today, Eren is here to help! {have instead of can ?? } {but today I can get Eren to help!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.89,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,How exciting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Controlling a Titan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't done that since sealing the wall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I go berserk again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might be killed by the Levi Squad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he didn't see the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't even particularly\Ncertain of this in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment's on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hange...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't turn into a Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The wounds you got from\Nbiting yourself aren't healing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't turn into a Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,sealing Wall Maria and all \Nis nothing but a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so depressed, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this just means you're\Nmore human than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.60,0:23:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer this to hurrying \Nmatters and losing lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lance Corporal Levi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you transform without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Eld, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Prove to us that you're not \Nour—no, mankind's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your responsibility to do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.16,0:24:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you so much as dare twitch that arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment you do, your head will roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oluo! I'm telling you to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lance Corporal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.38,0:24:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please step away from Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.88,0:24:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, {\i1}you're{\i0} the ones who should step away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My instincts tell me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.97,0:24:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Eren?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make any funny moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Prove it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.35,0:24:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what's—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.27,0:24:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You think we can't kill you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.98,0:24:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.02,0:24:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.98,0:24:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To mankind, you're—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.56,0:24:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please shut up for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.19,0:24:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.90,0:24:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I touch that arm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.28,0:24:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.87,0:24:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.91,0:24:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.29,0:24:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hange!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.45,0:24:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.67,0:24:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,H...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.00,0:24:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.46,0:24:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's damn hot when there's no skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.34,0:24:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's super hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.26,0:24:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Squad Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.59,0:24:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.55,0:24:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, isn't it hot for you, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.39,0:25:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How exactly are you connected to that arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.18,0:25:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.06,0:25:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.10,0:25:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to pull my arm out quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.36,0:25:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Eren! No funny business!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.45,0:25:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.45,0:25:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Eren, that's too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.16,0:25:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much more I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.17,0:25:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lance Corporal...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.88,0:25:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.68,0:25:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not... too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.53,0:26:00.78,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Sorry for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.78,0:26:02.58,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,They finally let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.91,0:26:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Explaining to the higher-ups took some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.16,0:26:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.33,0:26:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.17,0:26:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A teaspoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.63,0:26:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.30,0:26:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren's Titan arm was holding onto this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.30,0:26:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And for some reason, there's no \Ndeformation from heat or pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.27,0:26:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anything come to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.48,0:26:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I was trying to pick\Nthat up when I transformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.40,0:26:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.57,0:26:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that could explain why you weren't\Nable to turn into a Titan before.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.37,0:26:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kill the Titans."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.12,0:26:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Defend against the cannon."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.70,0:26:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Lift the boulder."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.96,0:26:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In every instance, you had a clear\Ngoal before you transformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.84,0:26:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's likely that self-injury \Nisn't the trigger on its own;
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.51,0:27:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you need some sort of objective as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.39,0:27:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.43,0:27:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning into a Titan to pick up a spoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.22,0:27:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.73,0:27:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, you didn't act\Nagainst orders on purpose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.07,0:27:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.04,0:27:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.75,0:27:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.09,0:27:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.13,0:27:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, I'm surprised you\Ncan bite yourself like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.17,0:27:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the wrong call on our part.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.93,0:27:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our modest way of apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.18,0:27:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it really makes a difference though.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.98,0:27:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Our job is to keep you in check, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.02,0:27:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We made no mistakes about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.61,0:27:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too cocky, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.82,0:27:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.11,0:28:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We were too on edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.74,0:28:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be upset by our indiscretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.53,0:28:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But, despite that...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.16,0:28:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As we rely on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.41,0:28:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we also want you to rely on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.63,0:28:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.76,0:28:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,believe... in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.89,0:28:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Squad Leader Hange here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.39,0:28:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment subjects...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.98,0:28:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of the Titans were killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.78,0:28:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawney! Bean!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.54,0:28:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.16,0:28:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me this isn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.29,0:28:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our valuable experiment subjects...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.54,0:28:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.88,0:29:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.05,0:29:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit's still on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.34,0:29:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it all happened before sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.05,0:29:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When a guard noticed, they got away with \Ntheir three-dimensional maneuver device.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.85,0:29:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawney!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.43,0:29:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.73,0:29:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.85,0:29:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Military Police Brigade will take over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.81,0:29:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.73,0:29:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.11,0:29:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think the enemy is?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.66,0:29:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, forget I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.56,0:29:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When's the last time the shaft was replaced?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.94,0:30:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Six days ago, after the cleaning operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.77,0:30:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She checks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.28,0:30:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.40,0:30:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.45,0:30:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Krista Lenz of the 42nd Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.95,0:30:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll inspect your gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.74,0:30:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can be punished for killing a Titan too?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.66,0:30:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As strange as it sounds, \Nthose were valuable specimens.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.54,0:30:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, why are they searching \Nfor the culprit amongst us recruits?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.84,0:30:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everyone's exhausted from \Ncleaning up the battlefield until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.38,0:30:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit must've really hated the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.26,0:30:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.14,0:30:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But in this case, they pretty \Nmuch helped the Titans out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.27,0:30:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Their lust for revenge may have been sated,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.73,0:30:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but mankind will suffer for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.40,0:30:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot, so I think I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.07,0:30:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I saw a Titan, I seriously planned \Nto enlist in the Survey Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.03,0:30:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.66,0:30:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's the day we have to decide too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.71,0:31:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Jean seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.76,0:31:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to join the Survey Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.42,0:31:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.84,0:31:11.47,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Because of what happened to Marco...  {Even after  ?? }
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.47,0:31:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But... aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.60,0:31:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Of course I'm scared\Nof joining the Survey Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.02,0:31:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm different from that reckless idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.81,0:31:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.86,0:31:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already in the Survey Corps, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.11,0:31:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm not putting my life on \Nthe line because I was persuaded to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.49,0:31:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, this isn't a decision \Nsomeone else can make for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.79,0:31:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.29,0:31:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.54,0:31:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.17,0:31:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean of all people said he'd \Nenlist in the Survey Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.13,0:31:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.67,0:31:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're set on the Military Police Brigade, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.97,0:31:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I should go there too, shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.97,0:31:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, if someone told you to die, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.06,0:32:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.27,0:32:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.77,0:32:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why not decide for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.57,0:32:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.19,0:32:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that if there's a legitimate reason, \Nthere might be no other choice but to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.33,0:32:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't like it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.91,0:32:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.83,0:32:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.75,0:32:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.71,0:32:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.88,0:32:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weak, but you {\i1}do{\i0} have guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.42,0:32:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.26,0:32:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie, you're actually pretty nice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.97,0:32:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it seems like you don't\Nwant us to join the Survey Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.73,0:32:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason why you want to join\Nthe Military Police Brigade though?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.40,0:32:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.11,0:32:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.61,0:32:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to save myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.06,0:33:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.39,0:33:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oluo,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.56,0:33:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,may I go speak with my friends for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.77,0:33:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, just go already.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.81,0:33:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mikasa, Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.11,0:33:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.36,0:33:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like it's been forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.70,0:33:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, did they do anything terrible to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.20,0:33:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Like inspecting every bit of your body
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.58,0:33:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or causing you mental anguish?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.16,0:33:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.42,0:33:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That shorty went way too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.88,0:33:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay him back in kind someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.88,0:33:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not talking about \NLance Corporal Levi, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.38,0:33:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.63,0:33:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.09,0:34:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow, you're all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.31,0:34:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.68,0:34:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys here because...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.02,0:34:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, you enlisted?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.23,0:34:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else would we be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.65,0:34:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the only ones who picked the Military \NPolice Brigade are Jean, Annie, and Marco?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.07,0:34:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.24,0:34:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.95,0:34:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.74,0:34:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What... did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.12,0:34:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say Marco's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.00,0:34:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like not everyone \Ndies a dramatic death.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.09,0:34:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even know how he went down.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.72,0:34:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,349)}He died alone, without \Nanyone seeing or knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.68,0:34:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.85,0:34:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.19,0:34:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that, as a Titan, you tried to kill Mikasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.65,0:34:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind explaining yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.94,0:34:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.94,0:34:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren was trying to kill a fly—
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.36,0:35:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.58,0:35:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.29,0:35:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In my Titan form, I tried to kill Mikasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.29,0:35:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't really remember it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.46,0:35:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you weren't aware \Nyou had that power until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.67,0:35:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you lack the means to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.92,0:35:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.01,0:35:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.51,0:35:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the situation we're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.56,0:35:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll probably die without Eren \Never knowing, just like Marco did.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.31,0:35:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean, why are you driving \NEren into a corner like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.23,0:35:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Mikasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.20,0:35:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everyone can blindly die for Eren \Nlike you, without anything in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.12,0:35:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We expect something out of Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.00,0:35:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us know what to expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.00,0:35:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And whether it's worth our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.13,0:36:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,860)}So, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.68,0:36:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're seriously counting on you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.48,0:36:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.64,0:36:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, recruits, gather up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.90,0:36:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uniforms are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.22,0:36:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, we're departing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.02,0:36:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lured away all nearby Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.60,0:36:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty seconds until the gate is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.40,0:37:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In mere moments, mankind \Nwill advance once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.11,0:37:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us what you're made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.08,0:37:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.68,0:37:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.19,0:37:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We now begin the 57th expedition!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.48,0:37:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.54,0:37:55.12,Default,Change to Flac 5.1,0,0,0,,A 10-meter-class approaching \Nfrom ahead, on the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.12,0:37:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm quite interested in \Nthe contents of its stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.71,0:38:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave this to the support squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.55,0:38:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.84,0:38:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Too shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.64,0:38:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Defend the ranks!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.60,0:38:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't falter!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.98,0:38:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to the support squad and advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.65,0:38:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward! Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.11,0:38:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oluo, can they...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.74,0:38:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can my comrades beat the Titans?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.45,0:38:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.41,0:38:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell have you been \Ndoing this past month?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.92,0:38:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you damn brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.88,0:38:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,During an expedition,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.59,0:38:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the point is to {\i1}avoid{\i0} the Titans if possi—
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.60,0:38:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Assume the long-distance scouting formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.10,0:39:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, Armin.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.40,0:39:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wet yourself even if you run into a Titan!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.52,0:39:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.53,0:39:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.20,0:39:14.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1498.500000,865.500000)\fad(195,140)\b1\blur2\b1\fsp-0.750000\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Line 3-3: Relay
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.20,0:39:14.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1497.000000,862.500000)\fad(195,140)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur0.5\b1\fnCardo\c&HF1F1F1&}Line 3-3: Relay
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.58,0:39:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The vanguard will form a semicircle.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.24,0:39:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we're spread out,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.70,0:39:18.25,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(286.500000,693.000000)\fad(195,187)\b1\fsp-1.500000\blur2\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Line 5-Center: Standby
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.70,0:39:18.25,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(285.000000,690.000000)\fad(195,187)\b1\fsp-1.500000\blur0.6\fnCardo\c&HF3F3F3&}Line 5-Center: Standby
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.95,0:39:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,stay within eyesight of someone on all sides,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.75,0:39:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in fixed distances from one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.71,0:39:21.25,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1156.500000,363.000000)\fad(188,184)\b1\blur2\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Line 2-5: Relay
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.71,0:39:21.25,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1155.000000,360.000000)\fad(188,184)\b1\blur0.5\fnCardo\c&HF3F3F3&}Line 2-5: Relay
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.38,0:39:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Extend survey and relay range as far as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.21,0:39:24.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(406.500000,300.000000)\fad(191,181)\b1\blur2\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Line 3-4: Relay
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.21,0:39:24.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(405.000000,297.000000)\fad(191,181)\b1\blur0.5\fnCardo\c&HF3F2F0&}Line 3-4: Relay
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.09,0:39:27.92,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1291.500000,259.500000)\fad(189,1600)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur2\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Line 2-4: Relay
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.09,0:39:27.92,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1290.000000,256.500000)\fad(189,1600)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur0.5\fnCardo\c&HF3F2F0&}Line 2-4: Relay
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.03,0:39:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.45,0:39:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.66,0:40:02.29,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1599.000000,565.500000)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur2\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Line 1-8: Scout
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.66,0:40:02.29,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1597.500000,562.500000)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur0.6\fnCardo\c&HE6E7E7&}Line 1-8: Scout
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.76,0:40:13.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1585.500000,726.000000)\fad(191,181)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur2\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Line 2-Center: Command
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.76,0:40:13.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1584.000000,723.000000)\fad(191,181)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur0.6\fnCardo\c&HE6E7E7&}Line 2-Center: Command
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.57,0:40:28.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1585.500000,693.000000)\fad(188,179)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur2\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Line 2-3: Relay
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.57,0:40:28.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1584.000000,690.000000)\fad(188,179)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur0.6\fnCardo\c&HE6E7E7&}Line 2-3: Relay
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.00,0:40:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Red... Red smoke signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.38,0:40:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Blouse! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.39,0:40:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.22,0:40:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we missed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.97,0:40:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's draw it toward us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.89,0:41:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Blouse! Come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.57,0:41:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.61,0:41:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.49,0:41:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.76,0:41:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Squad Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.09,0:41:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back in position!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.55,0:41:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.27,0:41:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.18,0:41:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been a while since the red \Nsmoke signal was fired,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.65,0:41:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but we've yet to regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.81,0:41:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.44,0:41:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A black smoke signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.53,0:41:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is one ignoring nearby people and heading \Nstraight for the formation's center?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.49,0:42:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.79,0:42:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.20,0:42:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}an Abnormal!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.83,0:42:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, guess we have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.34,0:42:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sys, you get its nape!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.63,0:42:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop it in its tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.22,0:42:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.09,0:42:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arlert should be over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.72,0:42:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to let a new \Nrecruit run into one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.10,0:42:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll kill it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.78,0:42:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Sys!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.91,0:42:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Squad Leader Ness did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.75,0:42:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We got it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.88,0:42:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You came for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.25,0:42:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.21,0:42:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Shallot!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.68,0:43:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.10,0:43:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the right flank scout squad doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.69,0:43:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If it ignored them and came this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.61,0:43:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,then it must be an Abnormal too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.27,0:43:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.82,0:43:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sys, let's do it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.74,0:43:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.53,0:43:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, to think we have \Nto do this twice in a row...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.54,0:43:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And it looks like it's a 14-meter-class at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.41,0:43:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This one will be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.71,0:43:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.97,0:43:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.18,0:43:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it get to Arlert!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.14,0:43:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sys!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.35,0:43:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.55,0:44:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.13,0:44:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.43,0:44:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.93,0:44:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll die too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.01,0:44:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.60,0:44:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.16,0:45:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.88,0:45:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.34,0:45:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She took off my hood...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.59,0:45:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and looked...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.84,0:45:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,at my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.64,0:45:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.89,0:45:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.76,0:45:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.23,0:45:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for starters, you're dead meat if \Nyou don't have a horse outside the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.69,0:45:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.69,0:45:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.32,0:46:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,From the right flank?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.41,0:46:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean we got hit \Nso bad we can't continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.20,0:46:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we lost part of \Nthe right flank scout squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.37,0:46:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hordes of Titans came.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.17,0:46:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same direction she came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.75,0:46:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.75,0:46:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she leading the Titans here?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.21,0:46:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,An Abnormal?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.63,0:46:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's a human controlling a Titan's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.55,0:46:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.72,0:46:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment her vitals were targeted,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.81,0:46:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,she flung Sys to the ground, crushing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.98,0:46:41.19,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,Regular Titans will only consume.{doesn't sound right ?!! talking about femal Titan?} {She didn't kill to consume.} {Regular Titans will only consume."}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.48,0:46:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling she's looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.49,0:46:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming that's true, \Nshe must be searching for...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.20,0:46:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.41,0:46:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.99,0:46:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Levi Squad, which Eren's in,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.74,0:46:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,should've been in charge of the \Nright flank that she passed through.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.41,0:46:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.75,0:47:00.79,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,They should be in the safest spot of this formation. {should probably ?? } {most likely ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.67,0:47:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess they're somewhere in the center rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.63,0:47:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, we don't have time to think right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.59,0:47:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,At this distance, we might still be able to draw her attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.18,0:47:18.02,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,We might be able to buy enough time for everyone else to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.31,0:47:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.48,0:47:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I... know what needs to be done now!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.77,0:47:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, this is the job we chose!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.94,0:47:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.08,0:48:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.17,0:48:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She covered her nape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.05,0:48:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.21,0:48:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn, I can't get away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.09,0:48:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.93,0:48:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.89,0:48:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Avenge that reckless idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.89,0:48:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Armin?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.60,0:48:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She stopped moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.81,0:48:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.06,0:48:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one that killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.65,0:48:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He really ended up dying on the right flank!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.69,0:48:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Avenge that reckless idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.08,0:48:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reiner?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.83,0:49:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It crushed my best friend with one stomp!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.83,0:49:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw his body stuck under its foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.92,0:49:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's going straight for the nape?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.17,0:49:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, that might work!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.10,0:49:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.82,0:49:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.74,0:49:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiner, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.51,0:49:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We bought enough time, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.76,0:49:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get away from her already!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.22,0:50:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't eat people, \Nshe shouldn't follow us!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.07,0:50:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.07,0:50:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The giant bitch got scared \Nand is running home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.70,0:50:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.95,0:50:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's toward the center rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.45,0:50:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could she be...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.04,0:50:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}heading toward Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.14,0:50:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it, why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.35,0:50:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reiner's horse came back,\Nso why is mine still missing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.38,0:51:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.71,0:51:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.26,0:51:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.30,0:51:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With two horses, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.43,0:51:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.02,0:51:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Krista!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.98,0:51:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.98,0:51:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.40,0:51:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.24,0:51:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Bufpart.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.53,0:51:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was extremely panicked when it ran to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.74,0:51:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you fight a Titan?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.04,0:51:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.33,0:51:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.87,0:51:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.96,0:51:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.88,0:51:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad our smoke signal got through to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.67,0:51:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to be nearby, \Nand Jean's horse was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.17,0:52:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even horses seem fond of you, \Nso I think you have some special charisma.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.89,0:52:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.64,0:52:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.02,0:52:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you all managed to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.23,0:52:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A deity...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.49,0:52:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.57,0:52:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.07,0:52:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we need to hurry back to the formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.70,0:52:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,808)}Oh, right. Withdrawal orders \Nshould be relayed soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.63,0:52:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A green smoke signal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.67,0:52:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the operation's continuing \Nwith just a change in direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.09,0:52:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.05,0:52:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we be withdrawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.80,0:52:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going through \NCommander Erwin's head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.68,0:52:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me the command squad \Ndidn't see the smoke signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.77,0:52:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the reason, it's obvious \Nwhat we should do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.90,0:52:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's obey the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.78,0:53:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Green smoke signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.78,0:53:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oluo, you fire it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.95,0:53:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.79,0:53:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems like everything's \Ngoing smoothly for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.08,0:53:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.38,0:53:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is that {\i0}really{\i1} the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.21,0:53:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.09,0:53:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an operation report!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.38,0:53:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The right flank's scouts \Nhave suffered heavy losses!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.26,0:53:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Scouting ability is crippled!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.14,0:53:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please relay this report to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.18,0:53:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that, Petra?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.06,0:53:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.93,0:53:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.73,0:53:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The right flank?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.65,0:53:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's where Armin should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.69,0:53:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A black smoke signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.49,0:53:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,An Abnormal!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.95,0:53:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, you fire it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.62,0:53:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.66,0:53:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.04,0:53:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We let them too far into the formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.42,0:53:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Titans are right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.88,0:54:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoever it is fighting under that smoke signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.51,0:54:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The right flank is all but annihilated, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.89,0:54:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're still not withdrawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.68,0:54:17.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(294.000000,621.000000)\fad(1500,0)\b1\blur2\fsp-0.750000\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Line 3-1: Transport
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.68,0:54:17.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(292.500000,618.000000)\fad(1500,0)\b1\blur0.5\fsp-0.750000\fnCardo\c&HE5E5E5&}Line 3-1: Transport
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.60,0:54:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.43,0:54:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.64,0:54:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.10,0:54:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, relay it to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.99,0:54:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.41,0:54:33.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1614.000000,430.500000)\b1\blur2\fsp-0.750000\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Line 1-13: Scout
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.41,0:54:33.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1612.500000,427.500000)\b1\blur0.6\fsp-0.750000\fnCardo\c&HEAEAEA&}Line 1-13: Scout
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.86,0:54:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been heading east for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.74,0:54:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The old town area should \Nbe to the south though.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.91,0:54:38.67,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1560.000000,588.000000)\b1\blur2\fsp-0.750000\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Line 1-5: Scout
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.91,0:54:38.67,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1558.500000,585.000000)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur0.6\fnCardo\c&HEAEAEA&}Line 1-5: Scout
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.45,0:54:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we'll run straight {\i1}there{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.79,0:54:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's in plain sight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.09,0:54:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The forest of giant trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.76,0:54:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Titans have passed through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.26,0:54:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing growing on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.52,0:54:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The wagons should have no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.77,0:55:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Relay this to the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.73,0:55:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the center line—the wagon \Nescort squad—will enter the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.44,0:55:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.04,0:55:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Squad Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.87,0:55:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the center line \Nis following the forest path.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.38,0:55:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we'll run into the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.09,0:55:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.76,0:55:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.10,0:55:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All soldiers, halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.97,0:55:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.43,0:55:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.10,0:55:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll now position ourselves to intercept.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.60,0:55:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Draw your blades and wait in the treetops.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.65,0:55:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If a Titan attempts to enter \Nthe forest, stop it at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.65,0:55:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.07,0:55:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Squad Leader, why—
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.99,0:55:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and obey!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.12,0:55:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.79,0:55:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.50,0:56:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,5-meter-class incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.30,0:56:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lance Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.59,0:56:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lance Corporal Levi!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.51,0:56:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.80,0:56:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"What", you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.06,0:56:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.10,0:56:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If only the center line enters the forest like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.94,0:56:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we won't know if a Titan is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.48,0:56:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like something's \Ncoming from the right,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.07,0:56:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but how will we avoid it \Nor protect the wagons?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.19,0:56:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit whining about the obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.28,0:56:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's clearly no way \Nwe can do either of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.80,0:56:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A black smoke signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.97,0:56:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.68,0:56:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the thing that came from the right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.97,0:56:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, draw your blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.02,0:57:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be over in an instant once it appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.63,0:57:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.31,0:57:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.02,0:57:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to avoid it in this forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.85,0:57:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's catching up!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.14,0:57:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lance Corporal, let's switch to \Nthree-dimensional maneuvers!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.81,0:57:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lance Corporal!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.15,0:57:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.19,0:57:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Reinforcements from the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.21,0:58:12.96,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to turn into a Titan and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.59,0:58:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Eren?!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.26,0:58:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That should only be done when \Nyour life is in grave danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.93,0:58:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you promise us that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.19,0:58:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.19,0:58:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.36,0:58:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.57,0:58:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the right answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.49,0:58:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.37,0:58:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I believed in myself
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.58,0:58:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the decisions of the comrades \Nwho've earned my trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.20,0:58:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the result was always a complete mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.21,0:58:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.58,0:58:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you should just do your best to \Nmake a decision you won't regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.98,0:59:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.23,0:59:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.92,0:59:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.75,0:59:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.38,0:59:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide already!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.50,0:59:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.68,0:59:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Target is accelerating!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.77,0:59:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.93,0:59:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll outrun it!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.41,1:00:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.93,1:00:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After securing the horses up ahead,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.39,1:00:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,switch to three-dimensional maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.48,1:00:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll act separately for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.73,1:00:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eld will take charge of the squad.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.65,1:00:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Could they be...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.70,1:00:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,capturing that Titan... alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.58,1:00:50.45,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,It sounds like something \Nis going on inside the forest.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.96,1:00:52.00,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,It's just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.54,1:00:55.00,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,I think the commander
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.00,1:00:59.51,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,was planning to capture that female Titan from the beginning, and baited her into this forest. { baited/lured her ?? }
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.51,1:01:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,To be precise, it's to capture the human inside it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.89,1:01:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Erwin's goal...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.89,1:01:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,was that all along.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.94,1:01:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it was, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.02,1:01:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But new recruits like me aside,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.32,1:01:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,why did they not tell Survey \NCorps veterans like all of you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.32,1:01:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.65,1:01:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you implying that we're not trusted by the Commander and the Lance Corporal?!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.70,1:01:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just as Eren said.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.54,1:01:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the Commander had a \Nreason for keeping this from us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.83,1:01:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A transforming human...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.38,1:01:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps, a spy who's working \Nwith such a person is amongst us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.01,1:01:49.56,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,But how many soldiers do you think died?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.56,1:01:54.64,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,If we knew that there was a Titan spy in our ranks,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.64,1:01:56.94,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,things should have gone differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.27,1:02:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he wasn't mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.44,1:02:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The lives of a hundred comrades
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.44,1:02:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,or the lives of all those within the walls...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.32,1:02:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Commander made his choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.45,1:02:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He decided to cast off the \Nlives of a hundred comrades.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.95,1:02:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, won't you come out already?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.25,1:02:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have all day, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.71,1:02:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken, you killed \Nmy subordinates in various ways,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.59,1:02:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but did you take joy in any of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.68,1:02:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.27,1:02:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.60,1:02:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right if I sever your hands and feet?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.48,1:02:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll grow right back, won't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.86,1:02:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about your real body.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.24,1:02:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a problem if you die, after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.73,1:03:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.89,1:03:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quite the scare.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.52,1:03:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Erwin, it smells.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.28,1:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Direction?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.28,1:03:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple, from every direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.49,1:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.04,1:03:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're targeting the female Titan?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.25,1:03:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Titans from every direction!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.55,1:03:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All soldiers, engage the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.68,1:03:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Defend the female Titan!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.94,1:04:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.70,1:04:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All soldiers, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.49,1:04:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Assume the formation.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.37,1:04:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to Karanese District!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.89,1:04:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been had.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.73,1:04:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.98,1:04:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you—
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.65,1:04:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This shows the enemy was prepared \Nto abandon everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.74,1:04:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To think they'd have themselves devoured \Nto avoid leaking information...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.04,1:05:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call up my squad.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.25,1:05:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Levi.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.34,1:05:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Resupply your blades and gas.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.42,1:05:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're short on time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.92,1:05:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What I have on hand should last.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.59,1:05:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.97,1:05:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an order.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.51,1:05:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Obey.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.68,1:05:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, Erwin.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.85,1:05:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll trust your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.57,1:05:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.74,1:05:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.95,1:05:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we really get them?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.12,1:05:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.12,1:05:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do much.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.00,1:05:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You believed in us, remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.63,1:05:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you stuck with us then \Nthat we arrived at this result.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.80,1:05:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rather difficult to make \Nthe right decision, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.31,1:06:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.35,1:06:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be from Lance Corporal Levi.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.94,1:06:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet up with the Lance Corporal!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.16,1:06:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Erwin.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.33,1:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you have Levi resupply?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.25,1:06:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.21,1:06:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The female Titan was devoured.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.17,1:06:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But... did you see the person inside get eaten?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.63,1:06:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.09,1:06:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.97,1:06:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.97,1:06:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you deduced before,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.47,1:06:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,if they're a type that can move to some \Nextent even after transforming...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.52,1:06:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.69,1:06:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,assuming they had a three-dimensional \Nmaneuver device equipped...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.98,1:06:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lance Corporal Levi?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.36,1:06:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not him!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.11,1:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.91,1:07:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.75,1:07:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunther!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.34,1:07:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.97,1:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.85,1:07:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunther is...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.89,1:07:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.81,1:07:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.94,1:07:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the female Titan?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.40,1:07:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Or were there others?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.77,1:07:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The female Titan?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.02,1:07:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way... How?!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.50,1:07:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.92,1:07:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.50,1:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the female Titan!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.34,1:08:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, why you...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.14,1:08:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it this time!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.51,1:08:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill it!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.60,1:08:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.85,1:08:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us will take \Ndown the female Titan.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.60,1:08:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You continue heading to HQ at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.73,1:08:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.02,1:08:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You doubting our skills?!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.49,1:08:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.32,1:08:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really that unreliable?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.25,1:08:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe my squad will be victorious!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.92,1:08:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.15,1:09:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We blinded it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.49,1:09:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It won't be able to see for at least a minute!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.24,1:09:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll finish it before that!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.49,1:09:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To hell with capturing it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.82,1:09:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll kill it now!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.62,1:09:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Die a dog's death here!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.91,1:09:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Down with this damn Titan!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.67,1:09:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll slice all of the muscles around your shoulders \Nso you won't be able to hold up your arms!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.64,1:09:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Slice them apart...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.77,1:09:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And those arms...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.02,1:09:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will drop!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.57,1:09:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're down!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.61,1:09:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the neck!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.28,1:09:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the muscles supporting its neck are cut...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.74,1:09:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we can get its nape!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.28,1:09:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your nape is mi—
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.58,1:09:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Eld!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.09,1:10:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.34,1:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't possibly see already!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.55,1:10:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even thirty seconds have...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.18,1:10:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one eye?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.68,1:10:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It prioritized one eye to heal faster?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.35,1:10:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that possible...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.81,1:10:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.40,1:10:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right yourself already!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.15,1:10:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.20,1:10:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.04,1:10:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.30,1:10:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.63,1:10:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My blade won't go through.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.74,1:11:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.74,1:11:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.79,1:11:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,kill it!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.59,1:11:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.76,1:11:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.68,1:11:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This voice...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.10,1:11:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.78,1:13:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I made the wrong decision...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.41,1:13:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I wanted to believe in my comrades...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.91,1:13:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}everyone died!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.09,1:13:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only I had believed in myself \Nfrom the start and fought...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.14,1:13:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only I had killed her from the start!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.19,1:13:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll rip you apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.86,1:13:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll split you wide open...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.74,1:13:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tear you to bloody shreds...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.16,1:14:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mangle every last chunk...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.12,1:14:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And devour it all!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.11,1:16:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.05,1:16:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.10,1:16:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.56,1:16:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.23,1:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Eren... back!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.95,1:16:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.26,1:17:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't the blade go through?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.02,1:17:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!{Stop!}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.73,1:17:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What're you...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.44,1:17:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall back for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.11,1:17:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Maintain this distance.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.11,1:17:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stick to a single objective.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.61,1:17:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we'll give up on killing the female Titan.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.74,1:17:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But they've killed so many of our comrades!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.45,1:17:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it can reinforce \Nits skin, we have no chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.87,1:17:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust my judgment.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.17,1:17:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll place our hopes on Eren being alive
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.59,1:17:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and rescue him before it gets out of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.22,1:17:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hack away at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.97,1:17:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You draw its attention!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.32,1:18:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.44,1:18:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So fast that it doesn't have time to reinforce!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.50,1:18:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can get the nape.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.88,1:19:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can kill it!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.30,1:19:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.31,1:19:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.53,1:19:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.65,1:19:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're pulling out!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.95,1:19:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.62,1:19:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.03,1:19:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Alive, at least!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.24,1:19:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Filthy though.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.62,1:19:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.87,1:19:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're retreating.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.57,1:20:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't there fewer of them than in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.79,1:20:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They've lost quite a few.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.00,1:20:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet another disaster.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.25,1:20:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They made a real racket when they left\Nin the morning, but they're back already.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.46,1:20:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd they go for?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.92,1:20:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, you shouldn't get up yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.34,1:20:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.80,1:20:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Survey Corps is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.47,1:20:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They get beaten so badly, \Nbut they keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.61,1:20:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Erwin! Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.65,1:20:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did this expedition achieve something \Nworthy of the sacrifices?!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.57,1:20:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you convinced the dead have no regrets?!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.62,1:21:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The expedition's expenses and \Ncasualties were more than enough
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.54,1:21:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to utterly humiliate the\NSurvey Corps' power base.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.22,1:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Those responsible, including Erwin,\Nwere summoned to the capital,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.31,1:21:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and Eren's new supervisor was chosen.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.78,1:21:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep at it, Annie!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.24,1:21:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's my girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.37,1:21:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Annie?!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.58,1:21:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No breaks!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.97,1:22:04.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961.500000,784.500000)\fad(529,0)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur2\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Wall Sina
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.97,1:22:04.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961.500000,850.500000)\fad(529,0)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur2\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Eastern Walled Town
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.97,1:22:04.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.000000,781.500000)\fad(529,0)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur0.6\fnCardo\c&HEFEFEF&}Wall Sina
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.97,1:22:04.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.000000,847.500000)\fad(529,0)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur0.6\fnCardo\c&HEFEFEF&}Eastern Walled Town
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.52,1:22:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh? You haven't heard?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.02,1:22:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seems like the Titan brat and his chief \Nsuperiors were summoned to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.64,1:22:08.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961.500000,918.000000)\fad(646,0)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur2\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Stohess District
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.64,1:22:08.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.000000,915.000000)\fad(646,0)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur0.6\fnCardo\c&HEFEFEF&}Stohess District
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.61,1:22:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be coming through here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.53,1:22:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.65,1:22:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure they'll end up \Ndissecting him this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.99,1:22:18.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961.500000,784.500000)\fad(527,391)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur2\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Stohess District
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.99,1:22:18.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961.500000,850.500000)\fad(527,391)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur2\fnCardo\c&H000000&}Military Police Brigade Branch Office
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.99,1:22:18.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.000000,781.500000)\fad(527,391)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur0.6\fnCardo\c&HEFEFEF&}Stohess District
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.99,1:22:18.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.000000,847.500000)\fad(527,391)\b1\fsp-0.750000\blur0.6\fnCardo\c&HEFEFEF&}Military Police Brigade Branch Office
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.91,1:22:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's finally up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.16,1:22:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you look so scary when \Nsleeping that I didn't dare wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.54,1:22:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.34,1:22:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been slacking off too much lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.84,1:22:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.01,1:22:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mad already, are we? Come on...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.30,1:22:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let her be.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.09,1:22:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie's from Trost District of all places.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.93,1:22:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the only one with battle \Nexperience in this branch.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.06,1:22:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't expect her to recover so soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.81,1:22:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, she's fresh out of living hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.07,1:22:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to cut that stuff out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.78,1:22:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you'll be assigned to do \Nsomething outside your usual duties.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.41,1:23:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I had you assemble here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.74,1:23:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the group of Survey Corps members \Nthat were summoned to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.91,1:23:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be passing through \Nthe town's central street today.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.25,1:23:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Military Police Brigade HQ \Nis in charge of escorting them,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.00,1:23:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're only tasked with helping \Non their leg through town.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.17,1:23:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Move alongside the escort squad \Nand work to bolster their security.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.72,1:23:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.91,1:23:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.38,1:23:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.84,1:24:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really part of the Military \NPolice Brigade now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.93,1:24:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.51,1:24:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the outfit?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.39,1:24:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a baggage carrier.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.27,1:24:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm using this rain coat to hide my \Nthree-dimensional maneuver device.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.02,1:24:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.11,1:24:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.49,1:24:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie, will you give us a hand \Nin helping Eren escape?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.07,1:24:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.16,1:24:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After rebelling against the monarchy, \Nwhere within the walls will you run to?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.58,1:24:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only going to hide out temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.17,1:24:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't plan to oppose them head-on.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.50,1:24:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be reported as an act of rebellion \Nby part of the Survey Corps,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.42,1:24:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but that'll buy us time
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.80,1:24:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,during which we'll prepare what's needed to \Noverturn the commission of inquiry's decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.30,1:24:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Without fail.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.01,1:24:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Does something that convenient exist?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.10,1:24:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Any leads?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.65,1:24:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.53,1:25:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to tell you this, \Nbut it's out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.82,1:25:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't say anything though, so do what you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.08,1:25:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.20,1:25:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.49,1:25:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Eren will be killed!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.25,1:25:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorant people, for their own self-preservation,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.09,1:25:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,are unwittingly attempting to set \Nhumanity on a path to extermination!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.51,1:25:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this isn't convincing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.76,1:25:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.22,1:25:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,all we can do is take a huge gamble now!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.60,1:25:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.44,1:25:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really seem like such \Na good person to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.11,1:25:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A good person?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.57,1:25:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.65,1:25:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't particularly like that term.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.65,1:25:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that just...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.36,1:25:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,seems like something you'd call \Nsomeone who's of use to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.04,1:25:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think there's anyone \Nwho's of use to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.54,1:25:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, if you don't agree to cooperate...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.05,1:26:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd be a bad person in my eyes, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.73,1:26:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.15,1:26:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.91,1:26:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We got through more easily than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.46,1:26:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Military Police Brigade for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.54,1:26:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear they work hard day after day.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.67,1:26:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit looking around.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.75,1:26:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll just have to hope they \Ndon't notice it's Jean in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.88,1:26:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't expect that to work long.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.80,1:26:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us look nothing alike, after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.47,1:26:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.85,1:26:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you have a villainous glint in \Nyour eyes and similar, evil-looking faces.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.10,1:26:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a horse face like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.15,1:27:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if I had decided not to help you, \Nhow were you planning to get over the wall?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.19,1:27:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We planned to get past using \Nthree-dimensional maneuver devices.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.24,1:27:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.70,1:27:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with, running before \Nentering Stohess District
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.78,1:27:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,would've saved you a lot of trouble, no?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.25,1:27:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why here and now?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.71,1:27:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I predicted the complicated terrain in this city
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.88,1:27:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,would make the switch more likely to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.71,1:27:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And rather than being openly defiant,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.92,1:27:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,feigning obedience would decrease suspicion
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.01,1:27:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and buy us more time to escape.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.60,1:27:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.35,1:27:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.27,1:27:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.11,1:27:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.28,1:27:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.33,1:27:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We go through here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.04,1:27:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The ruins of an underground city that \Nwas planned and abandoned still lie here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.54,1:28:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This path continues up \Nuntil near the outer gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.38,1:28:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.30,1:28:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.80,1:28:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.59,1:28:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not about to tell us that you're \Nscared of dark, narrow spaces, are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.10,1:28:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.35,1:28:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.14,1:28:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure a brave and reckless idiot like you
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.48,1:28:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't understand the \Nfeelings of a frail girl like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.86,1:28:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl who can flip a massive guy \Naround in mid-air isn't frail.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.66,1:28:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit joking and let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.08,1:28:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.46,1:28:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of going that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.42,1:28:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're not moving above \Nground, you're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.43,1:28:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.35,1:28:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over here already!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.77,1:29:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.02,1:29:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.48,1:29:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, isn't it, Mikasa?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.94,1:29:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Since for a while now,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.73,1:29:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,there hasn't been anyone \Naround for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.29,1:29:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.83,1:29:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.08,1:29:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when did you come to
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.63,1:29:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,look at me with such eyes,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.13,1:29:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.72,1:29:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie, why...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.85,1:29:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,480)}did you have Marco's \Nthree-dimensional maneuver device?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.64,1:29:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Down to the slightest scratches and dents...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.15,1:29:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,475)}Because we maintained our equipment together...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.57,1:29:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I recognized them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.11,1:29:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.28,1:29:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.12,1:29:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,something I found.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.74,1:30:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you suspected something a month ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.46,1:30:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't you do anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.79,1:30:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.42,1:30:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to believe I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.42,1:30:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.26,1:30:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But... you too...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.14,1:30:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,519)}Back then... Because you didn't kill me...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.43,1:30:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it came down to this, don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.49,1:30:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I completely agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.53,1:30:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined you'd end up \Ncornering me to this extent.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.41,1:30:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.83,1:30:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.30,1:30:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Annie!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.92,1:30:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still a chance you're an idiot
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.59,1:30:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,who has terrible timing with stupid \Njokes that you carelessly throw
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.34,1:31:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,into the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.39,1:31:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, just get down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.27,1:31:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can prove something by \Nsimply stepping down here!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.35,1:31:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So come here and prove it!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.27,1:31:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.94,1:31:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've... failed to become a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.94,1:31:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, this isn't funny at all!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.95,1:31:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk this through, Annie!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.24,1:31:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can still discuss—
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.32,1:31:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.37,1:31:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't listen to this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.54,1:31:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a waste of my time.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.75,1:31:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll slice you to shreds again...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.25,1:31:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Female Titan!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.03,1:32:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, it's great that I was \Na good person to you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.83,1:32:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gamble paid off this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.92,1:32:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.75,1:32:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see if {\i1}my{\i0} bet...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.59,1:32:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,pays off!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.44,1:32:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.45,1:32:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.11,1:32:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We were too late!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.21,1:32:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.09,1:33:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Our plan is for the day after tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.31,1:33:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,during our passage to the capital where \Nwe are to answer the summons—
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.02,1:33:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,at Stohess District.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.85,1:33:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be our first and last chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.23,1:33:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wager everything on this plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.74,1:33:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan is as follows:
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.95,1:33:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As we pass through Stohess District,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.70,1:33:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren will act as bait and lure the target \Nto this underground passage.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.16,1:33:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon bringing them to the lowest level, \Njudging by their size and power,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.21,1:33:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,their movements should be fairly \Nrestricted, even if they transform.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.04,1:33:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.21,1:33:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So the main target is, without a doubt, \Nin Stohess District, correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.84,1:33:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.80,1:33:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The target is part of the \NMilitary Police Brigade.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.18,1:33:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Military Police Brigade?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.60,1:33:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin was the one who inferred that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.68,1:33:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,According to him,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.18,1:33:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the Female Titan may be responsible \Nfor killing the two Titans we'd captured
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.31,1:34:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and is possibly a member of the \N104th Training Corps, like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.36,1:34:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait just a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.78,1:34:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of the female suspected \Nto be the Female Titan is...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.91,1:34:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.62,1:34:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.96,1:34:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Leonhart.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.09,1:34:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh... Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.76,1:34:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.60,1:34:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That ring...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.10,1:34:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So she saw through me from the start, after all!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.10,1:34:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She even noticed the ambush we planned too.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.11,1:34:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.23,1:34:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Status of the primary capture?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.65,1:34:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Unsuccessful!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.24,1:34:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please switch over to Plan B!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.99,1:34:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.79,1:34:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She stomped through?!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.83,1:34:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to save them!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.75,1:34:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, get back!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.67,1:35:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.09,1:35:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Female Titan trying to show \Nshe doesn't need Eren alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.76,1:35:08.43,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,If we stay like this, there's no telling when we're going to be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.05,1:35:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll figure something out,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.72,1:35:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,like how I was able to block cannon fire that time.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.93,1:35:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.94,1:35:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He—
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.81,1:35:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.98,1:35:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick close to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.53,1:35:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.03,1:35:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.70,1:35:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.62,1:35:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.37,1:35:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.13,1:35:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have a clear objective, \Nyou can't transform, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.26,1:35:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Visualize and focus on it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.47,1:35:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.76,1:35:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.02,1:35:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep down...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.64,1:36:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you're still hesitant to fight Annie, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.27,1:36:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.19,1:36:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're still thinking
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.90,1:36:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're mistaking Annie as the Female Titan.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.74,1:36:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not see what happened earlier?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.29,1:36:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman's the one who \Nkilled our comrades, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.08,1:36:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still not see that?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.50,1:36:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.71,1:36:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see I'm trying?!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.09,1:36:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie's the Female Titan?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.93,1:36:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.22,1:36:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that, Armin?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.69,1:36:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Female Titan knew what \NEren looked like from the start.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.90,1:36:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, she reacted upon hearing \NEren's nickname, "the reckless idiot",
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.94,1:36:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,when only our generation \Nshould know about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.74,1:36:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all else,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.07,1:36:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie was likely responsible for the murders \Nof Sawney and Bean, the test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.58,1:37:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.50,1:37:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Advanced techniques were required \Nto pull off those murders,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.75,1:37:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so she must've used her three-dimensional \Nmaneuver device, which she's proficient with.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.46,1:37:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.46,1:37:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's what the equipment inspection was for.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.97,1:37:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie came out clean.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.80,1:37:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because the device \NAnnie had was Marco's.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.47,1:37:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.52,1:37:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have just been seeing things?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.10,1:37:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was definitely something I—
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.52,1:37:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid, we've already heard that.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.86,1:37:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything else?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.77,1:37:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I know of.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.19,1:37:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that Annie's face \Nresembles the Female Titan's.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.86,1:37:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.78,1:37:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.91,1:37:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, has anything come to \Nmind after hearing all this?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.42,1:37:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When you fought hand-to-hand \Nwith the Female Titan,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.63,1:37:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,did it use any techniques \Nthat are unique to Annie?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.07,1:38:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.16,1:38:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Female Titan is Annie.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.71,1:38:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, shouldn't you be fighting?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.04,1:38:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.63,1:38:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is some particular emotion hindering you?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.97,1:38:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.22,1:38:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.93,1:38:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa and I will exit from that hole \Nand the entrance simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.85,1:38:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing so will force Annie to focus on one of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.11,1:38:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, Eren, follow the one she ignored.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.57,1:38:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.03,1:38:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that mean one of you will die?!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.78,1:38:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying here will get all three of us killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.83,1:39:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa, get in position!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.62,1:39:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take the front.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.75,1:39:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.96,1:39:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.09,1:39:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.84,1:39:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you two still fight?!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.63,1:39:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.39,1:39:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What choice do we have?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.10,1:39:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is a cruel place.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.08,1:39:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.98,1:40:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let the Female Titan get away!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.94,1:40:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stop her from getting out no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.36,1:40:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.52,1:40:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to save you!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.74,1:40:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.58,1:40:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's off.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.29,1:40:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There seemed to be some sort of explosion and—
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.91,1:40:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nile.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.54,1:40:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispatch all your soldiers at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.83,1:40:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We should assume a Titan has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.63,1:40:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.84,1:40:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Wall Sina, you know!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.92,1:40:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for a Titan to appear here!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.68,1:40:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.43,1:40:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, Jaeger!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.55,1:40:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of playing doppelgänger!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.48,1:40:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever call me that again, retard!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.35,1:40:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, let me go too!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.44,1:40:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your equipment from the 4th squad.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.61,1:40:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.82,1:41:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to be enthusiastic, but don't \Nforget to guard your own life.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.74,1:41:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.66,1:41:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Erwin!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.54,1:41:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on—
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.12,1:41:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone that can move, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.46,1:41:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll join the Female Titan capture squad!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.67,1:41:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Levi, you stay put.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.17,1:41:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You dislike meaningless death, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.17,1:41:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.55,1:41:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's mine or others'.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.05,1:41:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Titan! A Titan's here!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.55,1:41:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why here of all places?!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.85,1:41:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't they seal the wall—
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.06,1:41:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.47,1:41:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.18,1:41:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.06,1:41:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren is under this!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.31,1:41:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.27,1:41:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't he have transformed already?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.86,1:41:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't able to.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.28,1:41:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that Annie's the Titan \Nmight be what's hindering him.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.24,1:41:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.95,1:41:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to do something about {\i1}her{\i0} first!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.08,1:41:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.75,1:42:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are unable to abandon anything
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.59,1:42:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,will fail to bring about any change.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.84,1:42:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's required to overcome monsters,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.60,1:42:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,one must toss aside their humanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.06,1:42:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Annie is capable of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.89,1:42:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,those who can do so are victorious!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.66,1:42:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.53,1:42:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't kill me this time,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.08,1:42:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't be able to make excuses like \N"I'll see if {\i1}my{\i0} bet pays off!"
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.71,1:42:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, this way!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.00,1:42:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.01,1:42:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People who are unable to abandon anything
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.10,1:42:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will fail to bring about any change.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.23,1:42:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.73,1:42:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the time came...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.23,1:43:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clung to my comrades and the \Nbonds we shared, and failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.98,1:43:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Think back.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.33,1:43:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll... exterminate.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.71,1:43:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.29,1:43:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll kill!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.05,1:43:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have time to think about \Nwhether it's right or not!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.05,1:43:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just start by moving!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.97,1:43:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't get caught up in ideals!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.22,1:43:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.68,1:43:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.64,1:43:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The world's a cruel place!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.61,1:43:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.56,1:44:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.23,1:44:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eren...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.48,1:44:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A Titan?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.40,1:44:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why here?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.41,1:44:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's level ground!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.00,1:44:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Female Titan is approaching level ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.50,1:44:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't use our gear there!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.42,1:44:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Split into two groups and go around!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.21,1:44:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.05,1:44:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's a Titan—
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.52,1:45:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Annie...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.94,1:45:11.95,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{\i1}You always looked disinterested.{You always looked bored.}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.95,1:45:19.58,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, only when you were demonstrating your\N hand-to-hand techniques, you looked lively to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.12,1:45:23.38,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{\i1}You seemed like a terrible liar.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.38,1:45:24.83,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.71,1:45:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.84,1:45:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What in the world are you fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.39,1:45:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What great cause justifies killing people?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.99,1:46:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Annie...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.83,1:46:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Annie!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.60,1:47:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Annie...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.19,1:47:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At least know that Dad will be on your side.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.12,1:47:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll kill the Titans,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.26,1:47:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}not sparing a single one.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.83,1:48:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.91,1:48:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.79,1:48:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.42,1:48:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.21,1:48:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know if Eren can recognize you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.90,1:48:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... What...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.59,1:49:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What, the wall...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.01,1:49:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's climbing it?!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.82,1:49:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.15,1:49:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll get away at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.28,1:49:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no you don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.09,1:49:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.09,1:49:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.81,1:49:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Annie.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.60,1:49:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.81,1:49:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't ask you to forgive me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.78,1:50:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... I just have one favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.33,1:50:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Turn the entire world against you if you have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.96,1:50:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.25,1:50:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will destroy everything in the world!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.88,1:50:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if everyone in the world comes to hate you...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.26,1:50:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At least know that Dad will be on your side.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.68,1:50:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! He'll eat her real body too!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.85,1:50:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.48,1:50:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.65,1:50:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.15,1:50:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}free.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.86,1:50:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So promise me...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.53,1:50:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that you'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.80,1:51:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.81,1:51:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.77,1:51:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fusing?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.49,1:51:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.08,1:51:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't eat our valuable witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.87,1:51:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.16,1:52:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Erwin, we have quite a few concerns \Nabout the plan this time around.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.00,1:52:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had a target confirmed, why didn't you \Nseek the Military Police Brigade's assistance?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.25,1:52:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,District Chief, there was a need to carry out \Nthe plan with only those who could prove
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.97,1:52:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're not one of the Female Titan's allies, \Nwho are known to be lurking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.06,1:52:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.89,1:52:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you have some sort \Nof proof that you prevented
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.81,1:52:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind's demise through \Nthis extremely costly plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.94,1:52:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you can get anything \Nout of Annie Leonhart as she is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.65,1:52:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.66,1:52:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.37,1:52:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So in other words,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.28,1:52:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,this was all for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.41,1:53:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.30,1:53:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.01,1:53:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.47,1:53:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay enough to feel sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.93,1:53:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie's still sealed away, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.69,1:53:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.35,1:53:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.90,1:53:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We pull off such a large-scale \Noperation and gain nothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.40,1:53:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She went that far to withhold information.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.49,1:53:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.82,1:53:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.95,1:53:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.74,1:53:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw Annie, I couldn't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.96,1:53:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin Arlert,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.59,1:53:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean Kirstein,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.42,1:53:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to question you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.75,1:53:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.84,1:53:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Us first, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.30,1:53:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.13,1:53:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.65,1:54:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I thought it felt great.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.24,1:54:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if I felt refreshed \Nto have my body torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.07,1:54:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough for me to think \NI might as well die then.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.75,1:54:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.67,1:54:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not thinking that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.30,1:54:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you... came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.82,1:54:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.21,1:55:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.04,1:55:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I've grasped a great potential \Nwith which to save mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.30,1:55:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to the time when we couldn't even\N fathom humans transforming into Titans,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.72,1:55:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we've come a long way by\Nrestraining one of our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.81,1:55:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.81,1:55:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They're definitely out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.11,1:55:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us bring all of them to their knees—
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.78,1:55:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,all of the Titans within the walls.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.70,1:55:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's our turn to advance upon them!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.79,1:55:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Survey Corps and Eren Jaeger's \Nsummons to the capital were put on hold,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.13,1:55:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and custody of Annie Leonhart,\Nwho is being held deep underground,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.76,1:55:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was given to the Survey Corps.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.80,1:55:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.55,1:56:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for mankind to realize what \Nthey're being caged by,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.27,1:56:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}more time and sacrifices were still needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.54,1:57:15.13,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.38,1:57:17.55,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}What? Inside the wall...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.55,1:57:19.97,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fad(0,935)\fscy88\fscx88}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.34,1:57:22.05,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}It's a Titan!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.26,1:57:24.76,Default,NEW,20,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Squad Leader, your orders?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.22,1:57:27.22,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Huh... What?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.22,1:57:28.35,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}hold on just a second...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.94,1:57:39.61,Default,NEW,35,1020,266,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Don't let daylight\N shine on that Titan! {Do not let daylight shine on that Titan!}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.83,1:57:49.62,Default,NEW,35,1020,266,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Well, it's time you tell us\N now, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.41,1:57:53.33,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}What is this Titan?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.33,1:57:57.42,Default,NEW,35,1020,266,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Why is there a Titan inside\N the wall in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.42,1:58:03.38,Default,NEW,35,1020,266,,{\fscy88\fscx88}And why have you people\N kept quiet about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.35,1:58:09.39,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}I'm a busy man.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.39,1:58:12.02,Default,NEW,35,1020,266,,{\fscy88\fscx88}The church and my followers\N are in utter chaos,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.02,1:58:13.73,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}because of you guys!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.73,1:58:15.52,Default,NEW,35,1020,266,,{\fscy88\fscx88}I'll charge you on the\N amount of damage later!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.86,1:58:18.44,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.78,1:58:22.49,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Squad Leader...?!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.49,1:58:24.41,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.41,1:58:26.07,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Do you know why we,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.07,1:58:30.74,Default,NEW,35,1020,266,,{\fscy88\fscx88}the Survey Corps soldiers, \Nrepeatedly shed our blood?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.04,1:58:36.13,Default,NEW,35,1020,266,,{\fscy88\fscx88}It's to get back the freedom\N that the Titans stole from us!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.29,1:58:38.29,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.29,1:58:39.71,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}I'm not asking for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:39.71,1:58:42.26,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}I'm ordering you. Start talking.{I'm ordering you. Speak.}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.84,1:58:45.34,Default,NEW,35,1020,266,,{\fscy88\fscx88}And if you can't, \NI'll just go find another.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.34,1:58:49.51,Default,NEW,35,1020,266,,{\fscy88\fscx88}In any case, I don't think taking\N only your life will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.51,1:58:52.56,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Let go... of me...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.14,1:58:55.06,Default,NEW,35,1020,266,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Are you sure you want\N me to let go right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.06,1:58:56.56,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}It's useless...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.56,1:59:00.07,Default,NEW,35,1010,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Kill me and learn this for yourself...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.07,1:59:04.40,Default,NEW,35,1020,266,,{\fscy88\fscx88}We shall carry out our\N mission till the very end!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.40,1:59:05.57,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.57,1:59:11.37,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fad(0,1561)\fscy88\fscx88}let go of me right now!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.34,1:59:25.67,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Squad Leader...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.22,1:59:28.14,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Kidding, kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:28.14,1:59:29.18,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.14,1:59:34.68,Default,NEW,35,1020,335,,{\fscy88\fscx88}Say, Pastor Nick...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.65,1:59:43.23,Default,NEW,0,0,0,,{=0}{\fad(0,930)\fscy88\fscx88\move(467.5,760,776,1121,21,5568)\t(\fscx100\fscy100)}Are all these walls... full of Titans?{...are the walls all made of Titans?}{Are these walls... full of Titans?}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.74,1:55:44.00,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}See it on the people's faces everywhere
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.25,1:55:49.46,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Black'n'blue but they won't throw the towel in
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.46,1:55:53.88,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}And let go of a dream
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.34,1:55:58.80,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Man, women, child prepare to bleed
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.05,1:56:06.43,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Were we born to lose and let Goliath win?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.64,1:56:11.52,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Heavy air and screaming as you pull the pin
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.52,1:56:17.40,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,250)\blur3}Our world is collapsing but we can rebuild it
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.40,1:56:22.12,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}A 100 more years in the fire
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.74,1:56:28.33,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Do you believe that we can just kill them all?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.33,1:56:33.92,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Do you believe that we can conquer this?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.92,1:56:39.01,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Can't delete all the mess that I have seen
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.01,1:56:44.56,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Fall in the fire but these burns will heal you
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.72,1:56:50.48,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Gonna take your knives and skills they must be honed
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.15,1:56:56.44,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Show your mom your lives and give a dog a bone
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.44,1:57:01.20,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Just wait for centuries
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.20,1:57:05.37,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Man, woman, child long to be free
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.00,1:57:13.54,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}When we die we ask our brothers one more time
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.67,1:57:18.76,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}If the meaning of our lives was worth a dime
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.76,1:57:24.47,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Our world oxidizes but will surprise us
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.47,1:57:28.72,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}A 100 more years in the fire
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.85,1:57:35.27,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,250)\blur3}Do you believe that we can just kill them all?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.27,1:57:40.90,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,250)\blur3}Do you believe that we can conquer this?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.90,1:57:45.99,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Can't delete all the mess that I have seen
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.99,1:57:52.04,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Fall in the fire but these burns will heal you
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.04,1:57:57.63,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Coming down to show you what to do
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.63,1:58:03.30,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}How to die with honor, dignity
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.30,1:58:08.43,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}We should delete all the mess out from our sight
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.43,1:58:13.81,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}What is truth is for me and you
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.32,1:59:04.99,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,250)\blur3}Do you believe that we can just kill them all?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.99,1:59:10.20,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,250)\blur3}Do you believe that we can conquer this?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.20,1:59:15.25,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Can't delete all the mess that I have seen
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.25,1:59:21.42,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Fall in the fire but these burns will heal you
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.42,1:59:26.97,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Coming down to show you what to do
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.97,1:59:32.56,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,250)\blur3}How to die with honor, dignity
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.56,1:59:37.60,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,250)\blur3}We should delete all the mess out from our sight
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.60,1:59:44.15,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,1141)\blur3}What is truth is for me and you
